                            <comment id="17437886" author="sebx59" created="Wed, 3 Nov 2021 10:15:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I made a pull request on this one (sorry if I made some mistakes, It&apos;s my first time contributing to an apache project).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I modified the equals(TextStringBuilder) method so that it :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;checks that the other&#160;TextStringBuilder is not null&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;checks that both sizes are equals&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;send a substring of buffers to match the size to Arrays.eqals(), using ArrayUtils&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I updated the test case accordingly, initializing&#160;TextStringBuilder with different initial capacities&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
